description: Every card as a unique "atomic" object. May also be outputted as every card in a specific set. Some data properties will be omitted if they have differing values from set to set.
Every set and all cards in that set.
Each individual set file in a directory, compressed.
Every card type of any type of card.
All possible compiled outputs from MTGJSON, such as, AllCards, AllSets, Modern, SetList, etc.
All possible compiled pre-constructed deck outputs from MTGJSON.
List of all keywords used on Magic cards.
All sets, restricted to sets legal in Modern.
List of codes, names and release dates of all sets.
All sets, restricted to sets legal in Standard.
All sets, restricted to sets legal in Vintage.
Metadata object has date (OBDC standard) and version properties of this MTGJSON release.
